===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{liushu|p}} – pictogram of new shoots or leaves growing from {{zh-l|木}}; possibly the original graph of {{zh-l|㽕}}, with its upper part later extracted as {{zh-l|由}}.<ref>[1]田秋棉,陈絜.商周⿰㽕尋、寻、谭诸地的纠葛及相关历史问题之检讨[J].史学集刊,2021,(01):84-91.DOI:10.19832/j.cnki.0559-8095.2021.0007.</ref><ref>陳聞達：《釋甲骨文中的「㽕」、「𣡌」》</ref>

Alternatively interpreted as the upper part of the oracle-bone form of {{zh-l|柚}} (“pomelo”), depicting the fruit itself.<ref>王子楊《釋甲骨文中的“柚”》，《甲骨文字形類組差異現象研究》，中西書局，2013年，第287—307頁。</ref><ref>鄔可晶,施瑞峰.説“朕”“灷”[J].文史,2022,(02):5-44.DOI:</ref>

